{"tha-ap451:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap451:0.2":"Vibhitakavagga ","tha-ap451:0.3":"9 Vedikarakattheraapadana ","tha-ap451:1.1":"“Padumuttarassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap451:1.2":"Bodhiya padaputtame; ","tha-ap451:1.3":"Vedikam sukatam katva, ","tha-ap451:1.4":"Sakam cittam pasadayim. ","tha-ap451:2.1":"Atolarani bhandani, ","tha-ap451:2.2":"katani akatani ca; ","tha-ap451:2.3":"Antalikkha pavassanti, ","tha-ap451:2.4":"vedikaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap451:3.1":"Ubhato byulhasangame, ","tha-ap451:3.2":"pakkhandanto bhayanake; ","tha-ap451:3.3":"Bhayabheravam na passami, ","tha-ap451:3.4":"vedikaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap451:4.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap451:4.2":"byamham nibbattate subham; ","tha-ap451:4.3":"Sayanani mahagghani, ","tha-ap451:4.4":"vedikaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap451:5.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap451:5.2":"yam vedikamakarayim; ","tha-ap451:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap451:5.4":"vedikaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap451:6.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap451:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap451:6.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap451:7.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap451:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap451:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap451:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap451:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap451:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap451:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma vedikarako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap451:10.1":"Vedikarakattherassapadanam navamam. "}